 of body, voice, performance, caste, race, gender, and nation.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 05. Dez 2022) 0aDancexSocial aspectszIndia. 0aFeminism and dancezIndia. 0aFeminismzIndia. 0aWomen dancerszIndia. 0aWomen in the performing artszIndia. 0aWomenzIndiaxSocial conditions. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Feminism & Feminist Theory.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781478023760?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781478023760423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781478023760/original  aEBA_DUK_ALL  aEBA_DUK_EALL  aEBA_DUK_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles